**StreamTunnelArc**  
**Description:**  
Renders real-time data streams in a continuous arc-like scrolling chart optimized for visual clarity.

```markdown
# StreamTunnelArc - Curved Realtime Data Visualizer

StreamTunnelArc presents fast-moving numeric values on an elegant, curved scrolling path for dashboards or monitoring.

## Features
- Live arc-style chart  
- Real-time refresh  
- Built on Matplotlib

## Usage
```bash
git clone https://github.com/your-username/StreamTunnelArc.git
cd StreamTunnelArc
python visualize.py
